cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.RO 

This paper focuses on learning video representations using neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed method involves aggregating information from potential correspondences, which is related to multi-modal fusion (cs.MM) and attention mechanisms (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the robustness of the model to errors in proposals, which is relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and computer graphics (cs.GR).
